gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Bulls 112, Pacers 105
gameRecap.excerpt: The Bulls defeated the Pacers, 112-105. Nikola Vucevic recorded 24 points, 17 rebounds, and three assists for the Bulls, while Zach LaVine (23 points, five rebounds) and DeMar DeRozan (20 points, four assists) combined for 43 points in the victory. Myles Turner tallied 20 points and 11 rebounds for the Pacers in the losing effort. The Bulls improve to 2-2 on the season, while the Pacers fall to 2-1.
